Thank you for choosing BP Fit. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your information when you use our app. By using BP Fit, you agree to the practices described in this policy. If you have any questions, please contact us at [Insert Contact Information].

1. Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information:

We collect personal information you provide, such as your name, email address, and any other information you voluntarily share with us.
1.2 Health Information:

We collect health information such as pulse rate data, which is measured using the camera functionality on your device.
2. How We Use Your Information
Providing the Service: We use your information to deliver the app's functionality and features, such as measuring your pulse rate.
Analytics: We use your data to analyze and improve the app's performance and to develop new features.
Communication: We may use your email address to provide updates, respond to inquiries, and send other relevant communications.
3. How We Share Your Information
Third-Party Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers to perform tasks such as analytics and customer support. These providers are required to protect your information and only use it as directed by us.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to a valid legal request.
4. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.
5. Data Retention
We retain your data for as long as necessary to provide the services or as required by law.
6. Your Choices
Opt-Out: You can opt-out of receiving communications from us by following the instructions in any email you receive from us.
Access and Update: You can access and update your personal information within the app or by contacting us.
7. Children's Privacy
BP Fit is not intended for children under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
8. Changes to this Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the "Last Updated" date will be revised.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at info@codevicesolution.in.
Thank you for using BP Fit.
